# Result

Epic 2 was successfully completed by collecting the agricultural dataset, importing the necessary libraries, reading and validating the data, and performing comprehensive exploratory data analysis. These activities provided a thorough understanding of the dataset and established a strong foundation for data preprocessing and machine learning model development in the subsequent phases of the OptiCrop project.
